{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245070/extras/tevoran-smoke-scene.gif?t=1727309810\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245070/extras/story38.png?t=1727309810\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Edwin Tevoran, infamous mercenary leader and erstwhile (self-proclaimed) war hero, has found himself in a predicament. The dubious schemes which once filled his coffers have all succumbed to ill fortune, leaving him in penniless desperation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245070/extras/dialogue-steam.png?t=1727309810\" />However, when a serendipitous discovery spawns new designs for the petty criminality Tevoran loves so dearly, the door is opened to a chain of events that will forever change the course of the city of Tierva and beyond!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245070/extras/spinslash-steam.gif?t=1727309810\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245070/extras/gameplay38.png?t=1727309810\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Learn skills to unlock special attacks and abilities. Find, plunder, buy and sell items and equipment. Use terrain, traps, obstacles and even foes\u2019 corpses to your tactical advantage as you lead Tevoran &amp; Company to questionable victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245070/extras/characters-steam.png?t=1727309810\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.ste